doc.after: The city and its surroundings are served by Columbia Metropolitan Airport IATA CAE ICAO KCAE The airport itself is serviced by American Eagle Delta United Express and US Airways Express airlines In addition the city is also served by the much smaller Columbia Owens Downtown Airport located in the Rosewood neighborhood It serves as the county airport for Richland County and offers general aviation
